NNAAMMEE
     rraaiinn â€” animated raindrops display

SSYYNNOOPPSSIISS
     rraaiinn [--dd _d_e_l_a_y]

DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
     The output of rraaiinn is modeled after the VAX/VMS
     program of the same name.  To obtain the proper effect,
     either the terminal must be set for 9600 baud or the
     --dd option must be used to specify a delay, in
     milliseconds, between each update.  A reasonable delay
     is 120; the default is 0.

AAUUTTHHOORR
     Eric P. Scott

